snippet: Tight end Rob Gronkowski's season is over after the New England Patriots placed him on injured reserve on Saturday one day after he underwent surgery in Los Angeles to repair a herniated disk in his back....
lead_paragraph: Tight end Rob Gronkowski's season is over after the New England Patriots placed him on injured reserve on Saturday one day after he underwent surgery in Los Angeles to repair a herniated disk in his back.

headline.main: Patriots Tight End Gronkowski Out for Season
headline.print_headline: Patriots Tight End Gronkowski Out for Season
